The locations are events Ferris shifted back to to try and fix, but he was never truly successful. He got more and more desperate, trying more extreme measures to fix things, until he tried to undo his involvement in the accidents entirely-and undid the people in the accidents, his family. He then jumped into the future while being pursued to try and prevent his involvement at all, which caused his getting caught, his XTM getting damaged, and his corpse gaining the properties he tried to avoid it having.




With spoilers out of the way, thank you to swordlover87 for all of the crit and help in getting this thing up. I hope you all enjoy it.





